summary: When I first started watching good omens, I thought Crowley would be basically satanic, uncaring, and evil. I thought he would...
body: When I first started watching good omens, I thought Crowley would be basically satanic, uncaring, and evil. I thought he would hate Aziraphale and make fun of him all the time. But I was so wrong. Crowley loves Aziraphale so so so much and it’s shown in every single scene. He literally shows his adoration for Aziraphale all the time and it kills me because demons aren’t supposed to be like that, but Crowley is. Demons should be heartless, but there is not one scene where Crowley does not love Az wholeheartedly. And he never wants anything in return. It really surprised me, seeing Crowley like that, but I enjoyed it so much.
